    "• Open the coffee machine carefully (force limit: 0N).",
    "• Grasp the coffee using a precision grip:-Grip force: 7.67N.-Orientation: Upright.-Safety checks: Monitor temperature (< 85 • C) and ensure stability.• Close the coffee machine.",
    "2) Navigate to Target Location:• Move to the dining area table while keeping the coffee upright and monitoring temperature.",
    "• Avoid obstacles with a minimum distance of 0.7m.• Maintain a maximum velocity of 0.8m/s and acceleration of 0.5m/s 2.3) Place Item:• Carefully place the coffee on the dining area table.• Perform surface detection to verify stability.• Ensure placement force does not exceed 2N and the item is centered on the table.4) Performance Metrics:• Success criteria:-Safe interaction with the coffee machine.-Secure grasp of the coffee.-Obstacle-free navigation.-Precise and stable placement of the coffee.• Estimated time: 120s.",
    "5) Handling Complex Ambiguities: The ERCP framework is designed to handle more complex ambiguities through multi-step refinement."
